<div class="slide_question">
<h2>As you get older, you’re more likely to become:</h2>
</div>
<div class="slide_text">
<input id="q3" name="q3" type="hidden" value=""/>
<ul class="radio_inputs">
<li>
<a data-selected-answer="a" href="#">
<div class="answer_input_text">
<div class="input">a</div>
<p>A night owl</p>
</div> </a>
</li>
<li>
<a data-selected-answer="b" href="#">
<div class="answer_input_text">
<div class="input">b</div>
<p>An early bird</p>
</div> </a>
</li>
<li>
<a data-selected-answer="c" href="#">
<div class="answer_input_text">
<div class="input">c</div>
<p>A sleepwalker</p>
</div> </a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</li>
<li class="slide answer" data-slide-type="answer">
<div class="slide_content">
<div class="slide_media"> <div class="rmq_progress"><span class="cur_prog_title">Answer </span><span class="cur_prog_num">1</span>/<span class="tot_prog_num">12</span></div><div class="slide_question"><h2>As you get older, you’re more likely to become:</h2></div></div>
<div class="slide_text">
<ul class="rmq_answers">
<li class="user_answer">
<span class="answered_title"> </span>
<span class="you_answered_text">You answered: </span>
<span class="answer_text"> </span>
</li>
<li class="correct_answer">
<span class="answer_text_title">Correct Answer: </span>
<span class="answer_text"> </span>
</li>
</ul>
<div class="answer_expl">
<div class="expl_content">
<p>A change to your body’s internal clock may mean you’re up before the sun. Older people tend to fall asleep earlier at night and wake up earlier than they used to. This pattern is called advanced sleep phase syndrome. It might not be a problem, unless you miss out on nighttime fun with friends and family. If you need to reset your body clock, get out in the sunlight from late afternoon until sunset.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
