<div class="slide_question">
<h2>This is a common sleep disorder in older people:</h2>
</div>
<div class="slide_text">
<input id="q6" name="q6" type="hidden" value=""/>
<ul class="radio_inputs">
<li>
<a data-selected-answer="a" href="#">
<div class="answer_input_text">
<div class="input">a</div>
<p>Sleep apnea</p>
</div> </a>
</li>
<li>
<a data-selected-answer="b" href="#">
<div class="answer_input_text">
<div class="input">b</div>
<p>Restless legs syndrome (RLS)</p>
</div> </a>
</li>
<li>
<a data-selected-answer="c" href="#">
<div class="answer_input_text">
<div class="input">c</div>
<p>Both</p>
</div> </a>
</li>
<li>
<a data-selected-answer="d" href="#">
<div class="answer_input_text">
<div class="input">d</div>
<p>Neither</p>
</div> </a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</li>
<li class="slide answer" data-slide-type="answer">
<div class="slide_content">
<div class="slide_media"> <div class="rmq_progress"><span class="cur_prog_title">Answer </span><span class="cur_prog_num">1</span>/<span class="tot_prog_num">12</span></div><div class="slide_question"><h2>This is a common sleep disorder in older people:</h2></div></div>
<div class="slide_text">
<ul class="rmq_answers">
<li class="user_answer">
<span class="answered_title"> </span>
<span class="you_answered_text">You answered: </span>
<span class="answer_text"> </span>
</li>
<li class="correct_answer">
<span class="answer_text_title">Correct Answer: </span>
<span class="answer_text"> </span>
</li>
</ul>
<div class="answer_expl">
<div class="expl_content">
<p>Symptoms of sleep apnea, like snoring or pauses in breathing, can wake you up often during the night. (You may not know this is happening, only that you feel tired during the day.) RLS, which causes unpleasant tingling in your legs, is worse at night. And about 80% of people with RLS also have periodic limb movement disorder (PLMD), which makes your legs jerk every 20 to 40 seconds during sleep.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
