<div class="answer_expl">
<div class="expl_content">
<p>One large French study found that people were 26% less likely to report sleep problems in the first 7 years after retirement than in the 7 before. Men reported better sleep in those years than women. An Australian study found that retirement was linked to good lifestyle changes like exercising and sleeping more.</p>
