<li class="slide answer" data-slide-type="answer">
<div class="slide_content">
<div class="slide_media"> <div class="rmq_progress"><span class="cur_prog_title">Answer </span><span class="cur_prog_num">1</span>/<span class="tot_prog_num">12</span></div><div class="slide_question"><h2>For better sleep, the best time of day to exercise is:</h2></div></div>
<div class="slide_text">
<ul class="rmq_answers">
<li class="user_answer">
<span class="answered_title"> </span>
<span class="you_answered_text">You answered: </span>
<span class="answer_text"> </span>
</li>
<li class="correct_answer">
<span class="answer_text_title">Correct Answer: </span>
<span class="answer_text"> </span>
</li>
</ul>
<div class="answer_expl">
<div class="expl_content">
<p>Physical activity is important for your health as you get older, but timing is key. Your body temperature rises while you exercise and can take as long as 6 hours to drop. You’ll have an easier time falling asleep if your body is cooler.</p>
</div>
