<li class="slide answer" data-slide-type="answer">
<div class="slide_content">
<div class="slide_media"> <div class="rmq_progress"><span class="cur_prog_title">Answer </span><span class="cur_prog_num">1</span>/<span class="tot_prog_num">12</span></div><div class="slide_question"><h2>If you can’t fall asleep 30 minutes after going to bed, you should:</h2></div></div>
<div class="slide_text">
<ul class="rmq_answers">
<li class="user_answer">
<span class="answered_title"> </span>
<span class="you_answered_text">You answered: </span>
<span class="answer_text"> </span>
</li>
<li class="correct_answer">
<span class="answer_text_title">Correct Answer: </span>
<span class="answer_text"> </span>
</li>
</ul>
<div class="answer_expl">
<div class="expl_content">
<p>Don’t lie in bed tossing and turning. Go to another room, and do something soothing like reading or listening to music. Go back to bed once you feel drowsy. Don’t turn on the TV or use your computer or cell phone. The light from those devices can make it hard to fall asleep.</p>
</div>
